Usage: unsuppressMessage [-help] <prefix numId [numId2 ... numIdn]>

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
<prefix numId [numId2 ... numIdn]>     # Unsuppresses error or warning messages
                                       # identified by a unique ID.
                                       # Alternately, you can explicate name
                                       # each message by prefix-numId.
                                       # (string, required)